285
00:19:16.791 --> 00:19:19.827
-[Frank] You hear that. <i>güero?</i>
-[Rip] Shut the fuck up.

286
00:19:22.262 --> 00:19:23.731
You good?

287
00:19:24.565 --> 00:19:26.534
